This collection is a remix of several ork models rescaled, base and inflated to be printable with a resin printer for proxies for epic 40k games.

I printed all model. A few small details in some detailed miniatures may not come out or break during support removal but they don't affect the overall result.

I added to the lot a few custom bases designed for epic Armageddon.
